keyFacts: A phone call with Jeffrey Epstein was scheduled for January 11, 2019, from 16:00 to 16:30 UTC.
The calendar entry was created and last modified on January 9, 2019.
The call was classified as 'PERSONAL' and given a priority level of 5.
This scheduled communication occurred in early 2019, prior to Epstein's arrest in July 2019.
